WEBVTT

00:00.557 --> 00:01.793
I'm Zheng Li, special envoy

00:01.908 --> 00:03.389
from the people's Republic of China.

00:03.503 --> 00:05.212
As an ally, we are very powerful.

00:05.352 --> 00:06.670
An alliance, Sir?

00:06.814 --> 00:08.498
This administration will starve us out.

00:08.639 --> 00:10.425
You'll have your supplies in 48 hours.

00:10.594 --> 00:11.977
This is what the White House

00:12.086 --> 00:13.544
doesn't want anyone else to see.

00:13.655 --> 00:15.907
There are powerful people
organizing a coup d'etat.

00:16.064 --> 00:17.061
They've taken her somewhere,

00:17.182 --> 00:18.245
and I'm gonna find her.

00:18.372 --> 00:20.833
Sam.

00:20.957 --> 00:22.274
If you're with me, you're not safe.

00:22.378 --> 00:24.106
- I don't care.
- Yeah, I know. I do.

00:24.279 --> 00:25.705
Wait. Sam!

00:31.360 --> 00:32.567
Christine!

