01:02.869 --> 01:03.942
What's your status, Lieutenant?

01:04.095 --> 01:05.665
King has completed the weld repairs.

01:05.773 --> 01:07.196
First repair test positive.

01:07.293 --> 01:09.066
We're about to conduct
the deep dive test.

01:09.169 --> 01:10.953
It'll have to wait.
I need you back in port asap.

01:11.269 --> 01:12.252
Sir?

01:12.399 --> 01:13.514
The Chinese supply ship is headed

01:13.641 --> 01:14.915
towards us unescorted.

01:15.035 --> 01:16.809
The US has sent a destroyer
to intercept.

01:16.914 --> 01:18.211
They're not gonna let her
reach our shores.

01:18.382 --> 01:20.217
Also, there's a storm bearing down.

01:20.349 --> 01:21.987
Winds approaching typhoon strength.

01:22.118 --> 01:23.844
The situation on the island
has grown critical.

01:23.943 --> 01:25.470
We need that supply ship
to make it through.

01:25.661 --> 01:28.150
I need you in before it hits so
I can take command of the boat.

01:29.153 --> 01:30.084
Aye aye, Sir.

01:30.186 --> 01:32.775
Alert the crew. This will be
a combat patrol mission.

01:33.055 --> 01:34.179
All ahead flank, Lieutenant.

01:34.422 --> 01:36.936
Ahead flank, aye.
Colorado out.

01:46.705 --> 01:48.643
- Hi.
- Hi.

01:48.812 --> 01:50.278
I thought I might find you here.

01:50.465 --> 01:51.753
Yeah.

01:55.892 --> 01:58.341
Sam, I'm very sorry for your wife.

01:59.370 --> 02:01.208
If I can do anything...

02:03.248 --> 02:05.004
I don't know what to say.

02:09.368 --> 02:10.606
What is it?

02:13.222 --> 02:14.955
Who do you think you are to me?

02:15.392 --> 02:17.217
I'm trying to be your friend.

02:20.676 --> 02:22.447
You want to be friends?

02:23.219 --> 02:24.346
What do you think we should do, friend?

02:24.457 --> 02:25.610
You want-- you want to--
you want to--

02:25.713 --> 02:26.571
you want to jump in the sack?

02:26.685 --> 02:28.033
You want to screw the pain away?

02:28.137 --> 02:29.626
Is that what you want to do?

02:30.596 --> 02:32.671
Okay. Uh, I understand.

02:33.842 --> 02:36.024
I think there is a bit more
between us than that.

02:36.135 --> 02:37.190
Let's just be honest right now,

02:37.301 --> 02:38.560
'cause that's all I can deal with.

02:38.728 --> 02:40.430
We're not friends.

02:41.749 --> 02:42.962
Even right here, right now,

02:43.104 --> 02:44.630
what's going on between us,

02:44.759 --> 02:48.003
I promise you, this is not
how I feel about my friends.

02:48.490 --> 02:50.692
And I hate myself for it.
You get it?

02:50.800 --> 02:52.414
So you want to be my friend really?

02:52.531 --> 02:53.724
<i>Really?</i>

02:53.965 --> 02:55.503
Then you gotta leave me alone.

02:56.520 --> 02:57.961
Okay.

02:59.057 --> 03:00.458
I'm sorry.

03:00.570 --> 03:02.101
And, yes, I'll leave you alone.

