<i>7.</i>

03:13.405 --> 03:15.014
<i>90.</i>

03:15.196 --> 03:16.283
<i>4.</i>

03:16.532 --> 03:17.794
<i>11.</i>

03:18.381 --> 03:19.666
<i>Dolphin.</i>

03:20.314 --> 03:21.534
<i>9.</i>

